                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "isolating the Confederate states from the rest of the nation"
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "slowly and carefully readmitting southern states into the Union"
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_4",
